messages.home.hero_text: The tool which will help you automate client’s management effortless way and most importantly - absolutely FREE!
messages.home.steps.step1_text: Simply fill in registration form and verify your email.
messages.home.steps.step2_text: After verification, set up your working hours and you are ready to use your reservation management system.
messages.home.steps.step3_text: Brag about it in social media or wherever you want and wait for your customers reservations.
messages.home.benefits_title:
Meet nnizer, tool that
you’ll fall in 💛 with.
messages.home.benefits.benefit1_title: All your client’s reservation and data in one place.
messages.home.benefits.benefit1_text: Customers' bookings, their data, time and other customer details are displayed in simple and understandable way.
messages.home.benefits.benefit2_title: CRM built to be as simple and straightforward as possible.
messages.home.benefits.benefit2_text: Confirmation or cancellation of the reservation doesn't require notifying customers about it, everything is taken care of in advance.
messages.home.benefits.benefit3_title: Don’t spend any money on website, we got you.
messages.home.benefits.benefit3_text: Everything is free, no premium versions, no deceptions. Just sign up and use.
messages.home.benefits.benefit4_title: Never miss a chance because of language barrier.
messages.home.benefits.benefit4_text: Reservation management is available in both Lithuanian and English.

What're you waiting for?
Let's save some time!
